text: Chloé Maigre (born 24 December 1974) is a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Niamey
